    chapter: "Advanced Math - Medium",
    title: "Advanced Math 1",
    prompt: "A certain college had 3,000 students enrolled in 2015. The college predicts that after 2015, the number of students enrolled each year will be 2% less than the number of students enrolled the year before. Which of the following functions models the relationship between the number of students enrolled, *f(x)*, and the number of years after 2015, *x*?",
