    wrong: [["9","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["11","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["17","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."]],
    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::f123456). Substitute 2 for *x* in the function: *f*(2) = 3(2)^2 - 2(2) + 1 = 3(4) - 4 + 1 = 12 - 4 + 1 = 13.",
    source: 'OpenSAT',
