    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::random_id_6). Substituting -2 for x in the function, we get: $f(-2) = 3(-2)^2 - 2(-2) + 1 = 3(4) + 4 + 1 = 12 + 4 + 1 = 17$",
