    wrong: [["x^4 + 1","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["x^4 + 2x^2 + 1","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["x^4 - 2x^2 + 1","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."]],
    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::8d3b424f). This expression is in the form of the difference of squares: (a + b)(a - b) = a^2 - b^2. In this case, a = x^2 and b = 1. Therefore, (x^2 + 1)(x^2 - 1) = (x^2)^2 - 1^2 = x^4 - 1.",
