    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::6b4ebc8c). Since the expressions have the same denominator, we can combine the numerators: $\\frac{2x+3}{5} + \\frac{x-1}{5} = \\frac{2x + 3 + x - 1}{5} = \\frac{3x + 2}{5}$.",
