    chapter: "Problem-Solving and Data Analysis - Medium",
    title: "Problem-Solving and Data Analysis 385",
    prompt: "A group of friends is planning a trip. They decide to rent a car for the trip. The cost to rent a car is a flat fee of $25, plus $15 per day. Let *c* represent the total cost, in dollars, and *d* represent the number of days the car is rented. Which of the following equations represents the relationship between *c* and *d*?",
