    chapter: "Standard English Conventions - Medium",
    title: "Standard English Conventions 2",
    prompt: "The researchers concluded that, in fact, as many as half of the hunters in the groups they studied were female. This finding was a direct challenge to the accepted view that female participation in hunting was negligible.\n\nWhich choice best combines the sentences at the underlined portion to create a grammatically correct and stylistically effective sentence?",
