    prompt: "The text claims that the \"rise of the global middle class\" is a major factor in the increased demand for coffee. The text also mentions that in the past, coffee was \"associated with privilege,\" but today it is \"more widely consumed.\" What is the main idea of the passage?\n\nThe passage primarily suggests that",
