    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::random_id_25). The author explicitly states that \"the constant barrage of information, much of it negative and often sensationalized, can lead to a sense of overwhelm and anxiety.\" This directly suggests that social media can contribute to a sense of overwhelm and anxiety in young people.",
