    chapter: "Standard English Conventions - Medium",
    title: "Standard English Conventions 254",
    prompt: "The band's recent album, \"The Light in Our Shadows\", is a powerful and moving reflection on themes of loss, hope, and resilience. The music, however, ______ the lyrics, which are often introspective and deeply personal, suggesting a strong connection between the band's musical style and their experiences.\n\nWhich choice completes the text so that it conforms to the conventions of Standard English?",
