    wrong: [["explain how to perform the larger process.","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["illustrate the complexity of the larger process.","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["suggest that the larger process is not very important.","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."]],
    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::2a49c11d). The text describes the importance of one step of a larger process. This suggests that the author is emphasizing the importance of the particular step. The author is likely using the example to help the reader understand why this step is important.",
