    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::f8977781). The author’s argument that \"digital media makes us more conscious of the artificiality of the real\" directly supports the claim that the current generation of students has a more complicated understanding of reality than previous generations. The author is arguing that digital media has had a profound effect on how students understand reality, which has made their understanding more complicated.",
