    wrong: [["The study found that the majority of participants who did not use the program reported that it would have been \"helpful\" to their work. The participants who did use the program also reported that it was, \"helpful\" to their work.","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["The study found that the majority of participants who did not use the program reported that it would have been \"helpful\" to their work; the participants who did use the program also reported that it was \"helpful\" to their work.","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."],["The study found that the majority of participants who did not use the program reported that it would have been \"helpful\" to their work, the participants who did use the program also reported that it was \"helpful\" to their work.","This is one of the OpenSAT distractors, but it misses the specific evidence or calculation.","Use the passage, grammar rule, or math relationship named in the question rather than the closest-sounding option."]],
