    chapter: "Standard English Conventions - Easy",
    title: "Standard English Conventions 354",
    prompt: "A scientist is writing about the origins of Earth's oceans. The scientist wants to include a sentence that describes the chemical composition of early oceans. Which of the following sentences would best accomplish this?\n\nWhich of the following sentences would best fit in the paragraph above?",
