    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::666672cc). Choice B is the best answer because it describes the chemical composition of early oceans, which is relevant to the scientist's topic. Choices A, C, and D describe other characteristics of early oceans, but they aren't as directly related to the scientist's focus on chemical composition.",
