    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::b7a981b2). The word \"wonder\" at the end of the passage suggests that the speaker is reflecting on the passage, considering its meaning and implications. It creates a sense of contemplation and wonder, which is reinforced by the shift in tone throughout the passage.",
