    chapter: "Standard English Conventions - Medium",
    title: "Standard English Conventions 534",
    prompt: "“The sun,” he wrote, “is a giant ball of burning gas that provides warmth and light to the earth, and without it, no life could exist on our planet.”\n\nWhich choice best corrects the punctuation errors in the sentence?",
