    chapter: "Information and Ideas - Hard",
    title: "Information and Ideas 784",
    prompt: "The text presents an argument about the impact of digital technologies on the human mind. The author argues that the increasing reliance on digital devices is leading to a decline in cognitive skills, such as memory and attention. The author cites research findings suggesting that, for example, individuals who spend more time looking at screens are less able to recall information from memory. In this context, what is the significance of the information in the passage that the author cites research findings to support his claim about the impact of digital technologies on the human mind?\n\nThe author’s use of research findings in this passage is most likely intended to",
