    chapter: "Expression of Ideas - Medium",
    title: "Expression of Ideas 788",
    prompt: "The passage describes a woman who is a successful writer and has many fans, but it also discusses the challenges of maintaining her privacy. She worries about the impact that her writing might have on her loved ones. The speaker also discusses the challenges of navigating the expectations and pressures of being a public figure. What is the most likely reason why the author includes information about the speaker's worries?\n\nThe author most likely includes details about the speaker's worries in order to",
