    lesson: "Source: OpenSAT (opensat::876fc521). The author is emphasizing the speaker's conflicted feelings about fame and success. The speaker wants to maintain her privacy, but she also understands that her writing has a public impact. This creates a sense of tension and conflict for the speaker, which makes her a more relatable and interesting character.",
